name: Stranger nothings
description:
You suddenly came back to your senses, in the middle of the mall, having no idea what you were up to, or where you were going… 

Movement:

  • WASD | ZQSD: Move around.
  • Spacebar: Interact, move dialog forward.
  • Tab: Show the questlog.

Tools:

  • Unity
  • Aseprite
  • Tiled
  • FLStudio

!! Highly unfinished and buggy !!
